mer to go off every five minutes for say, two hours??<br>
<br>
Also I wasn't saying that it was worse than enchanter gather mana, just that it was similar in that way.  Despite the apparently small amount of actual time it takes to make use of the rods, using them to their fullest extent requires that you be very active.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>With the new, more efficient, rods, you can regen the damage a mod rod does before you are allowed to use it again (with regen 3 or mage self buffage or sitting most of the time).<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Yes, with the new rods the damage taken is fairly negligible.  <br>
